{"tid":2517699,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論] 第74屆康城影展 Cannes 2021","createTime":"2021-05-05T13:04:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-06T03:24:05.000Z","uid":121740,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"47d670064b3201eacb200c188ac9692c86de712b","tid":2517699,"uid":121740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resize-media.festival-cannes.com/fit-in/2560x1620/media_image/0001/74/f94788eb87ac41aa9f31f779bf48779b5eeac398.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresize-media.festival-cannes.com%2Ffit-in%2F2560x1620%2Fmedia_image%2F0001%2F74%2Ff94788eb87ac41aa9f31f779bf48779b5eeac398.jpeg&h=ab8903b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舉行：2021年7月6日至17日（當地）<br />\n藝術總監：Thierry Fr&eacute;maux<br />\n評審團主席：Spike Lee（美國）<br />\n片單公佈：5月27日（Press Conference） <br />\n<br />\n歷屆討論區（70th to 73rd）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913136</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1113989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1113989</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/625468/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/625468/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/245359/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/245359/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.festival-cannes.com/zh/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.festival-cannes.com%2Fzh%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn%2F4XLRjZdTHGp6sdrEQ6olc%3D&h=e1f1cc4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.festival-cannes.com/zh/</a> <br />\n<br />\n一同期待全球影壇年度盛事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da67d450002b6b1641be92e7fd2f3821da1da75","tid":2517699,"uid":121740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:06:03.000Z","msg":"已確認入選主競賽單元（Official Selection） <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">Paul Verhoeven《Benedetta》<br />\nLeos Carax《Annette》 </span><br />\n<br />\n繼早前公佈法國導演 Leos Carax 睽違九年首部英語電影《Annette》為康城揭開序幕的消息外，官方今日亦確認了名導Paul Verhoeven的《Benedetta》入選主競賽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdWiNyR2Jpjx9kdEcFX6aFetLRPBtn3NzyvyeB2kLW81M?filename=UAoYv4O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUAoYv4O.jpg&h=b70ffd9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由 Virginie Efira 主演、改編自 Judith C. Brown 的著作，講述17世紀意大利修女 Benedetta Carlini 經常產生幻覺，及後更與另一名修女發生關係的經過。 <br />\n<br />\n先行預告<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/n-31QJXV3iA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fn-31QJXV3iA&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn%2F4XLRjZdTHGp6sdrEQ6olc%3D&h=ef8d58cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/n-31QJXV3iA</a>"},{"pid":"ec32c508405f3a84d6451bbc533ab3a07448b0ac","tid":2517699,"uid":48479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:22:26.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢篇報導話PTA想去康城，但發行商傾向去威尼斯<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldofreel.com/blog/2021/5/ytjmen28sufns7l1sj1xa0m7ot0lti\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldofreel.com%2Fblog%2F2021%2F5%2Fytjmen28sufns7l1sj1xa0m7ot0lti&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn%2F4XLRjZdTHGp6sdrEQ6olc%3D&h=f1a18cf8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldofreel.com/blog/2021/5/ytjmen28sufns7l1sj1xa0m7ot0lti</a>"},{"pid":"5a3f8b4d995c8a97e3734a766e1b393197f649a8","tid":2517699,"uid":264685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:05:27.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f2251435695cef3c005c04b708c9d6b3d8af6f","tid":2517699,"uid":4260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://25.media.tumblr.com/548f3ef3156fa0960ce8e07942d1ad1c/tumblr_mhidmoPHUE1rot0kgo1_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F25.media.tumblr.com%2F548f3ef3156fa0960ce8e07942d1ad1c%2Ftumblr_mhidmoPHUE1rot0kgo1_500.gif&h=67f8130e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"494079472c1396097ae529276719aa09ad13639a","tid":2517699,"uid":121740,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T15:16:16.000Z","msg":"那些很有可能在康城亮相的有&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nMia Hansen-L&oslash;ve《Bergman Island》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTQkbKvGwxwhXUh6XbzoFakLTpgeHefERxASQ5hgHaxLC?filename=gR1vnT1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgR1vnT1.jpg&h=e594868a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據法國發行Les Films du Losange 的排片時間表，該片將於7月14日（國慶日）公映，恰好也正值影展舉行期間，料採取「康城+全法院線」同步上映。<br />\n<br />\n該片講述一對從事電影製作產業的美國夫妻（情侶）在夏季的時候來到了一座小島上為他們的下一部電影尋求劇本的靈感，而這座島也就是 Ingmar Bergman 曾經常居且永眠的「法羅島」。<br />\n<br />\n然而在隨著夏季以及他們所創作的電影劇本的發展，在於島上景色那現實與虛構之間的界線卻也逐漸的模糊&hellip;"},{"pid":"5691fca11b3d55f3cc88ccaf230b9a30ff0aca61","tid":2517699,"uid":121740,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T15:39:51.000Z","msg":"那些很有可能在康城亮相的有&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n濱口龍介《Drive My Car》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmac6wUR7ys6bgiUPiZoNoyD4UP7roPphJyFzPypnH67GL?filename=SnhRRP4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSnhRRP4.jpg&h=3a79b8e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年年頭憑《偶然與想象》斬獲柏林評審團大獎的濱口龍介，已經完成改編村上春樹短篇小說的新片，預定今年夏天日本上映，也很可能在康城作首映。<br />\n<br />\n西島秀俊飾演舞臺演員和導演家福悠介，原本想去理解和原諒外遇的心愛妻子，但對自己是越加痛苦，直到分手後崩潰，在喪失感中生活的他和沉默寡言的專屬司機渡利美咲（三浦透子）。描繪通過愛車Saab而相遇的孤獨的兩人，在到達一線希望之前的故事。"},{"pid":"ff82a1c6b255d7e32f86b212e8b2060db5ea094d","tid":2517699,"uid":48479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5691fca11b3d55f3cc88ccaf230b9a30ff0aca61","tid":2517699,"uid":121740,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T15:39:51.000Z","msg":"那些很有可能在康城亮相的有&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n濱口龍介《Drive My Car》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SnhRRP4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSnhRRP4.jpg&h=3a79b8e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年年頭憑《偶然與想象》斬獲柏林評審團大獎的濱口龍介，已經完成改編村上春樹短篇小說的新片，預定今年夏天日本上映，也很可能在康城作首映。<br />\n<br />\n西島秀俊飾演舞臺演員和導演家福悠介，原本想去理解和原諒外遇的心愛妻子，但對自己是越加痛苦，直到分手後崩潰，在喪失感中生活的他和沉默寡言的專屬司機渡利美咲（三浦透子）。描繪通過愛車Saab而相遇的孤獨的兩人，在到達一線希望之前的故事。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T15:56:32.000Z","msg":"早排讀咗原著，故事好適合濱口發揮，十分期待成品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af3cf7711be888684f50b0eaab457f702d4ef73","tid":2517699,"uid":121740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T16:58:46.000Z","msg":"那些很有可能在康城亮相的有&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nKirill Serebrennikov《Petrov's Flu》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd5JX11cegi6BNbAf84bPQ13ps6Qcfy2hH2J35v3JnG56?filename=SKFsqHf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSKFsqHf.jpg&h=864bb4f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n電影原本已確定將在去年康城影展中首映，理應也是主競賽單元，但在影展取消下決定延到今年再回康城參展。<br />\n<br />\n改編自作家 Alexey Salnikov 的小說作品，講述在後蘇聯時期中男主角 Petrov 和他的小家庭的生活。<br />\n<br />\nPetrov 是一位汽車黑手、而他的老婆則是一名圖書館員， 且他們還有一個小兒子，但是他們卻不住在一起。<br />\n<br />\n看似再平凡不過的家庭，但卻在流感肆虐之時讓一切的虛實界線開始爆炸，並且讓他們的生活陷了入瘋狂和超現實之中。"},{"pid":"27e53970b9bc0c126b58a4816f0b02dc76414dd9","tid":2517699,"uid":8075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T17:01:56.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd0a35e4077ba6038d0e9ba60d547d1a86019ac","tid":2517699,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T17:38:07.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b42ea37699eb3b5c76827442b27bae2338d87567","tid":2517699,"uid":58246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T17:45:42.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"f5432203157bc85397f1c660ed70a98dc696d320","tid":2517699,"uid":6436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2